Local, Site, Domain, OU OU OU 
    Multiple GPO in out link order is 3,2,1. Lowest number in the OU wins. 

Password policies are in default domain policy. Won't work elsewhere, not tested. 

Filtering for computers is required for computer configuration 

You can block inheritance for child OU. 

You can also enforce on parents which removes the ability to block inheritance. If enforced all child OUs will accept. What happends with Enforced > Enforced? 

Loopback processing mode if you need computer settings to override user GPO. 
